svg.metadata: Created by FontForge 20161116 at Thu Nov 6 16:53:24 2014 By Jimmy Warting I did not design this font completely, is loosely based on Lariata Typecafe. Traced from the 1993 edition of Novum Press book Schreibschriften/Script Types, compiled by Michael Rau & Rosemarie Kloos-Rau. I did add the punctuation marks for the book only had letters and numbers.
